channel.title: Uncalled Attack v5 - Project Insanity to Greatness
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img339.imageshack.us/img339/8832/uarise.jpg[/img][/center] [size=12pt][b]There is an anti-leech! If you can remove it, you have my permission to release the source, only on MoparScape, without the anti-leech.[/b][/size]
I got very bored with this source, so I decided it was best to just release it with an anti-leech. The anti-leech has to do with my new networking that's in this source. Remember, you [b]are[/b] allowed to release this source without the anti-leech, but [b]only [/b]on MoparScape.
We have better features than most Project Insanity servers that are released today. Look down at the features, not many? I said "better than" not "more than." I hope you enjoy this source, the hardest part of the project was implementing the NIO networking. I took hours to just add that, so that's why I decided to put an anti-leech in it.
It's an anti-leech that doesn't let you connect to the server, so you'll have to take some programming time in removing it. Thank you all for the support you gave me on the development and thank you for taking the time to read this. [hr] [hr] [size=14pt][b]Links:[/b][/size] Source: http://www.mediafire.com/?41jd800e3m4pa8p Client: http://uppit.com/lf6c9ne5dlrk/Uncalled_Attack_v5_Client.rar [hr] [hr] [size=14pt][b]Features:[/b][/size]
[ul][li]Better woodcutting base[/li] [li]Better firemaking base[/li] [li]Clipped firemaking[/li] [li]Clipped following[/li] [li]Combat updated[/li] [li]Very small networking update[/li] [li]New Watchtower training teleport[/li] [li]Edited quite a bit to have a great economy[/li] [li]Much faster switching[/li] [li]Completed classes[/li] [li]Fixed the general store dupe, you can still buy & sell items there[/li] [li]NIO Networking[/li][/ul]
[hr] [hr] [size=14pt][b]Videos:[/b][/size] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tbOQS5MUdAA[/youtube] [hr] [hr] [size=14pt][b]Pictures:[/b][/size] [img]http://img17.imageshack.us/img17/6538/uncalledattack201112152.png[/img] [img]http://img687.imageshack.us/img687/7979/uncalledattack201112171.png[/img]
